<ul class="reset smalltext" id="msg_1109481_extra_info">
<li class="postgroup">Guard<li class="stars"><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><img src="Themes/celeste/images/pip.gif" alt="*" border="0"/><li class="postcount">帖子数: 194<li class="karma">苹果币: 0<li class="profile">
